GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
H 1
HOUSE BILL 642
Short Title: Funds/Scotland Cty. Wastewater Improvements. (Public)
Sponsors: Representative G. Pierce.
For a complete list of sponsors, refer to the North Carolina General Assembly web site.
Referred to: Appropriations, if favorable, Rules, Calendar, and Operations of the House
April 2, 2025
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO APPROPRIATE FUNDS TO SCOTLAND COUNTY FOR WASTEWATER
3 TREATMENT PLANT IMPROVEMENTS.
4 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
5 SECTION 1. The sum of thirty-five million dollars ($35,000,000) in nonrecurring
6 funds for the 2025-2026 fiscal year is appropriated from the General Fund to Scotland County
7 for improvements or upgrades to the County's wastewater treatment plant.
8 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025.
